{"tid":2099411,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美日澳三國國防部對支那制定黨安法深表關注","createTime":"2020-07-08T08:08:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T20:05:20.000Z","uid":21470,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5b78dcfbdfb733f3c5afe3f27acde29075b71abf","tid":2099411,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T08:08:09.000Z","msg":"美日澳防長對北京制定港區國安法深表關注<br />\n<br />\n美國國防部長埃斯珀，同日本防衛相河野太郎及澳洲國防部長雷諾茲，召開視像會議後發表聯合聲明，一致同意就中方制定港區國安法深表關切，又表達強烈反對中方在東海和南海的活動日益活躍。 <br />\n<br />\n在東海問題，3國防長指存在&ldquo;改變現狀的威壓性行動&rdquo;，美日澳將加強安保合作，又強調會同東盟合作，構建太平洋地區伙伴。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2346026\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2346026&d=68p4wiGQQ1h%2Fwz3iobjDK5IBJzpNVIoVNH6FP0f0bDA%3D&h=31535862\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2346026</a>"},{"pid":"ab9a9dd44cc212ee9be9a5bf10e48cd9dfc4b90f","tid":2099411,"uid":273747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T08:09:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86b5f767074a5516e13fd2c5b0770119b79368ad","tid":2099411,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T08:11:12.000Z","msg":"國防部長都出聲"},{"pid":"cdbec9eca805a527abb86d4470d41a2ac97b124d","tid":2099411,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T08:21:57.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39f854d5a5ed0e7ba116c3007699b0591d78d0fb","tid":2099411,"uid":143343,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T08:23:01.000Z","msg":"澳門都出去埋聲"},{"pid":"e9f3e7bd7bd4a4c8e1ae4fc6dca0ae1d8a7e97d7","tid":2099411,"uid":121146,"like":0,